(39, '实训基地', '校企合作生产性实习实训基地建设方案', '<p><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">为深入落实湖南省人民政府办公厅转发省经信委、省教育厅等7部门《关于深入推进企业与职业院校合作办学的若干意见》(湘政办发〔2012〕45号)精神，大力推进我省职业院校校企合作生产性实训基地项目建设，加快建设一批对接我省优势特色产业和战略性新兴产业的校企合作生产性实训基地，特制定本方案。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　一、指导思想</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　全面贯彻落实党的十八大关于加快发展现代职业教育的精神，重点对接湖南</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">优势特色产业、战略性新兴产业</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">及“四大国家战略发展区域”发展需求，以职业院校</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">主体或特色专业为依托</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">，以校企深度合作为基础，按照“</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">基地建设企业化、实践教学生产化</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">”的总体要求，加快建设一批“</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">高水平、高效益、有特色、成规模</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">”，融产学研和社会服务功能于一体的校企合作生产性实习实训基地，推动全省职业院校实践教学水平和人才培养质量的提高，更好地服务“四化两型”和“四个湖南”建设。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　二、基本原则</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　1、统筹规划。根据我省优势特色产业和战略性新兴产业发展需求，结合长株潭城市群两型社会建设试验区、湘南承接产业转移示范区、武陵山片区国家扶贫攻坚示范区、洞庭湖生态经济区等四大区域板块发展对技术技能人才的需求，全省统筹规划，分步实施。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2、校企共建。探索实施学校提供场地，企业提供资金、设备、技术并全程参与基地建设与管理的实习基地建设模式，实现学校与企业信息互通、文化互融、人员互聘、资源共享。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　3、协同推进。以实训基地设备、技术不断更新为重点，校企协同开展实训体系建设、师资队伍建设、信息化资源建设，统筹基地功能发挥，不断提高实训基地建设水平和运行效益。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　4、开放共享。鼓励和支持校企合作生产性实习实训基地面向职业院校和社会开放，接受行业企业指导，开展交流合作，承接职业院校师生实习实训、行业企业生产经营和员工培训、职业技能鉴定等任务，充分发挥基地使用效益。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　三、建设目标</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">从2014年起，三年内全省共立项建设60个左右“产业契合度高、校企合作紧密、管理体制机制完善、实习实训指导教师水平高、教学资源丰富、社会服务能力强”的校企合作生产性实习实训基地</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">，带动全省职业院校创新实训基地建设模式，提高实践教学水平和人才培养质量。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　四、建设内容</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　（一）校企合作</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">体制机制建设<br/></span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　1、</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">建设模式</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">。校企合作生产性实习实训基地建设要以职业院校为主体，以</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">与规模以上企业</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">（指工科类）深度合作为基础，以</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">一个主体、特色专业及所属专业群为依托</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">，通过</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">“引企入校”，校企共建“校中厂”模式</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">的生产性实习实训基地；校企双方必须签署协议，明确资源配置、成本核算、收益分配、财产管理、师生实训等方面的责权利，并共同制定生产经营等方面的管理制度，形成以“契约”为保障的利益共享机制；基地参与合作的企业应具有一定的生产或经营规模，生产技术和工艺水平符合职业院校人才培养目标的需要；三年内</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">企业</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">对基地建设资金或设施设备的</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">投入应占到基地设备设施总投入的60%以上</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">，且企业规划对基地的总投入</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">文科类基地不低于100万元，工科类基地不低于200万元</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">，中职学校可适当降低；基地具有较强的实体化运作能力，能参与企业生产经营或拥有自办产业或开展行业企业员工培训；基地所有制产权明晰、以学校为主体，建设周期一般为3年。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2、</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">运行机制</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">。建立校企共同参与的管理机构，形成“</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">校企联动、合作育人、协作生产、共同研发</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">”的运行机制，实现学校教学环境与企业现场环境、学校文化与企业文化有机融合；企业主动提供真实的生产项目或经营案例，校企合作开发实训项目，基地生产性实习实训产品或教学案例80%以上来源于真实生产（经营）项目；企业生产、技术、标准、设备向基地院校无偿开放，形成校企专业技术人员定期换岗交流机制；基地教学功能突出，每年承担职业院校师生实习实训不少于6000人日。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　3、</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">管理模式</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">。成立基地院校与合作企业共同组成的管理机构，共同负责基地的建设与管理。将企业先进的管理理念、管理方法与职业文化引入基地，建立科学合理的管理模式和运行机制；实施基地院校统一管理下的“专业（群）+基地”运作模式，统筹发挥基地的教学、生产（经营）、培训、鉴定和技术服务功能；推行项目化实训，按照企业实际工作流程组织实训教学，学生和培训对象能参与基地实际项目的实施；以企业标准为依据，形成项目化、模块化教学培训标准，校企共同评定教学培训质量。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　（二）</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">硬件环境建设<br/></span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　1、</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">场地及设施设备</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">。基地场地及设施设备功能完备、技术先进、工位足够，能满足生产性实习实训和培训需要。基地场地及设施设备按照企业生产经营要求配置，具有真实的职业环境；设施设备配套，能满足综合性项目生产性实习实训需要；设备技术参数达到专业领域企业现场设备中等以上水平，设备完好率90%以上；基地场地及设施设备具有一定规模，同一项目能够同时满足50人以上生产性实习实训需要。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-varian