lvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">能力。基地具有一定的生产经营能力，并有一定的生产经营利润用于实习实训或培训。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　3、应用技术</span><span style="color:#ff0000;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">研究或推广</span><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">能力。基地开展应用技术研究或推广服务，为企业提供产品开发、工艺革新、技术推广服务或经营策划服务。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　五、申报、遴选与管理</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　（一）项目申报</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　1、申报基本条件。申报学校与专业除符合本文件规定的要求外，还应具备以下条件：（1）申报本项目的高等职业院校，必须是省教育厅备案的独立设置的高职学院；申报本项目的中等职业学校需经当地教育行政主管部门审核备案。（2）有下列情形之一者不得申报：①近三年有违规办学行为，造成不良社会影响的；②近三年出现重大安全责任事故或群体事件的；③国家有关职业教育建设项目验收未获通过的；④中职学校举办者在县级人民政府职业教育工作督导评估中“暂缓通过”或“不合格”的；⑤同一学校同一专业在“十一五”、“十二五”期间已立项为省级生产性实习实训（教师培训）基地（或为省级重点实习实训基地和专业课教师专业技能教学水平认证培训基地）的。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2.申报主体。校企合作生产性实习实训基地项目以学校为单位申报。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　3.申报材料。①申请报告；②项目申报表（见附2.1）；③项目建设实施方案（见附2.2）；④项目建设任务书（见附2.3）；⑤《校企合作共建生产性实训基地协议书》；⑥其他相关佐证材料。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　（二）项目遴选</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　1、专家评审。我厅组织专家进行评审，初选立项名单。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2、批准立项。初选名单由我厅审定后予以公示，公示无异议后发文批准立项。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　（三）项目管理</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　本项目纳入湖南省职业教育省级重点建设项目统一管理。我厅对本项目的建设给予一定的专项经费支持，项目院校要切实加强经费的使用管理，确保专款专用，提高经费使用效益。</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　附：2.1 湖南省职业院校校企合作生产性实习实训基地项目申报表</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2.2 湖南省职业院校校企合作生产性实习实训基地项目建设实施方案</span><br style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);"/><span style="color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(202, 155, 112);">　　2.3 湖南省职业院校校企合作生产性实习实训基地项目建设任务书</span></p>', '2016-01-26 21:40:03', '学院介绍', 3, '');
INSERT INTO `information` (`information_id`, `information_type`, `information_title`, `information_body`, `information_time`, `information_class`, `information_count`, `information_url`) VALUES
(40, '实训基地', '我校与临矿集团签订实训基地建设合作协议', '<p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">2</span><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">月<span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word">13</span>日，山东科技大学与临矿集团实训基地建设合作签约仪式在临矿集团举行。学校副校长张士强，临矿集团董事长、党委书记张希诚，副总经理郭修杰出席签约仪式。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">会上，双方一同观看了马坊煤矿实训基地建设宣传片，临矿集团副总工程师、地企联络办主任朱玉清对实训基地建设进展情况作了简要介绍，随后双方就校企合作事宜进行了交流。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">张士强在会上发表讲话，介绍了学校的基本情况，并阐述了双方此次合作的重要意义。他指出，高校对学生的培养离不开现场，离不开实践，学生的实习问题是制约人才培养质量提升的重要因素，通过与企业联合建设实训基地，将进一步促进教育教学改革，更好地实现人才培养目标。他说，在煤炭市场严峻的形势下，临矿集团仍然对教育事业慷慨帮助、无私奉献，对这种精神深表感谢。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">张希诚高度评价了学校与临矿集团长期以来友好合作所取得的成效，希望通过建设实训基地能协助学校培养具有较强实践应用能力的专业人才。他强调，此次协议的签订既是实施校企合作、人才强企战略的重要手段，也是促进企业产学研一体化的有效方法，将进一步推动临矿集团转型升级发展。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">最后，张士强与张希诚签订了山东科技大学与临矿集团实训基地建设合作协议。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)">学校教务处处长曹茂永、学生工作处处长诸葛福民、合作发展处处长王伟参加了活动。</span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;</p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: center;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-indent: 37px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;color: rgb(62, 62, 62)"><span style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word"><img width="595" height="268" style="line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word" alt="" src="http://news.sdust.edu.cn/attachment.php?AttachmentID=5B3153316D5BB9407933DC7A698591D6"/></span></span></p><p style="line-height: 20px;text-align: center;word-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Simsun;font-size: 13.3333px;font-style: normal;font-variant: normal;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: auto;text-indent: 0px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="line-height: 20px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-family: 宋体"><span style="line-height: 24px;text-align: justify;word-wrap: break-word;font-size: 16px">签约仪式现场</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-01-26 21:40:38', '学院介绍', 0, ''),
(41, '实训基地', '校企合作实习实训基地启动', '<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">3月18日，理工学校校外实习实训基地揭牌仪式在海盐恒通汽车服务有限公司隆重举行。教育局、交通局相关领导参加了揭牌仪式，并为“校外实习实训基地”揭牌。理工学校汽修专业实习学生和恒通公司员工一起见证了这一重要时刻。<br/>　　揭牌仪式上，恒通汽车服务有限公司徐建康总经理、理工学校何永香校长分别代表校企双方在揭牌仪式上致辞，双方都表示希望通过校企合作，以实习实训基地为依托，推进“工学交替”，加强汽修行业高技能人才的培养。以“共建、共享、合作、共赢”为原则，实现校、企优势互补，提高学校与企业需求的对接度，共建人力资源培养与储备的基地，提升中职毕业生就业能力，拓宽中职生就业渠道。<br/>　　目前，汽车成为了中国家庭日益普及的交通工具，对于汽修维修保养等方面专业人才需求已成为日益迫切需要解决的问题。恒通汽车公司是我县汽修行业有影响的知名企业，管理理念先进，技术力量雄厚，服务质量上乘。理工学校作为省一级重点职业学校、浙江省首批改革发展示范学校和省级职工培训示范基地，正是以此为依托，在上级各级政府和教育行政部门的高度重视和关怀下，与恒通汽车公司携手共建，为学校建立校外实习实训基地，这也是学校2013年推出的加强校企合作的重要举措之一。　<br/>　　整个揭牌仪式简短而隆重。校企双方将一起努力为海盐地方经济和社会事业发展作出应有的贡献。</span></p><p style="text-align:center;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img alt="" src="http://119.29.56.141/image/20160126/1453815697416964.jpg" border="0" hspace="0"/><br/><br/><img alt="" src="http://119.29.56.141/image/20160126/1453815698895152.jpg" border="0" hspace="0"/></p><p><br/></p>', '2016-01-26 21:41:39', '学院介绍', 0, ''),
(42, '实训基地', '我校召开校校合作实训基地研讨会', '<p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28.8px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">10月31日，为推进会计国示范创建工作，落实学校产教融合的人才培养模式，在教育局的组织领导下，来自省常中、一中、二中、三中、田家炳、民族中学、勤业中学、刘高职等学校的领导，在我校7号楼312会议室，就校校合作实训基地建设工作进行研讨。会议由教育局计财处纪忠处长主持。</p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28.8px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">首先由秦益霖校长介绍了我校各系部创建的一系列实训项目的概况，提出了当前职业教育产教融合的重要性。同时秦校长代表学校感谢教育局的大力支持，创建了“常州旅商常青藤公司”，为商贸类学生提供了真实的实训平台。紧接着，经贸系刘振华主任介绍了关于“常州旅商常青藤连锁实训超市”的前期准备工作。</p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28.8px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">随后各学校领导就校校合作创建连锁实训超市展开了具体的讨论，大家一致肯定了教育局和我校的创建实训平台的做法，同时他们对后期具体实施细节提出了非常宝贵的意见和建议。</p><p style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28.8px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);">最后大家达成共识：创建连锁实训超市是改革创新的举措、是三方共同受益的局面，本次研讨会达到了预期的效果。</p><p style="text-align:center;margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 28.8px; orphans: auto; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; font-size: 14pt;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: 宋体;"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; color: rgb(0, 106, 62); text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.czlsgz.com//attachment/cms/item/2014_11/03_18/851ea5fb67c4e4a5.jpg" target="_blank"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, weiruanyahei, 微软雅黑, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; border: none; text-indent: 0px; width: 600px; height: 426px;" alt="111.jpg" src="http://www.czlsgz.com//attachment/cms/item/2014_11/03_18/851ea5fb67c4e4a5.jpg.cthumb.jp